teran of the Afghan war, less adoring and more active.'),(11,'The Aldrich Family','[\"House Jameson\", \" Jackie Kelk\", \" Mary Malone\"]','Frank Papp, Ezra Stone','Clifford Goldsmith',7.8,'[\"Comedy\", \" Family\"]','1949-10-02','30 min','https://m.media-amazon.com/images/M/MV5BODBlNTNjNDctNmEyNi00NmRjLWE5Y2QtM2JkZjI0OGVlNjFhXkEyXkFqcGdeQXVyMjI5MDUyNDU@._V1_SX300.jpg',1,'Based on a popular radio show, this middle class American family comedy is built around the life of the Aldrich family of Elm Street, Centerville. In particular, the show focuses on the adventures of Henry, the Aldrich\'s high schooler son.'),(12,'The Food That Built America','[\"Campbell Scott\", \" Adam Richman\", \" Yohuru Williams\"]','Nick White','Brian Burstein, Yoshi Stone (head writer)',8.4,'[\"Documentary\", \" History\"]','2019-08-11','30S min','https://m.media-amazon.com/images/M/MV5BMTQwYTAxZjItODA5OS00YjhmLTk0NjYtNTVlMTNhMjBiMWVhXkEyXkFqcGdeQXVyOTEyMzc0NTc@._V1_SX300.jpg',1,'Food will tell the unknown stories of innovation and rivalries behind food industry tycoons Milton Hershey, John and Will Kellogg, Henry Heinz, C.W. Post, the McDonald brothers and more.'),(13,'Human Playground','[\"Idris Elba\", \" Kiki Bosch\", \" Amy Winters\"]','Tomas Kaan, Morgan Knibbe, Willem Timmers','Hannelore Vandenbussche',6.8,'[\"Documentary\"]','2022-09-30','1 min','https://m.media-amazon.com/images/M/MV5BZGZmOTM3YjYtYjkwMy00NmNkLWFlNmUtNmMwNTA1YmQyOWRiXkEyXkFqcGdeQXVyNDg0NjMwNDY@._V1_SX300.jpg',1,'This docuseries explores the origins and evolution of play across the globe, from age-old rituals to billion-dollar businesses.'),(14,'Dummy','[\"Anna Kendrick\", \" Meredith Hagner\", \" Donal Logue\"]','Tricia Brock','Cody Heller',6.7,'[\"Short\", \" Comedy\", \" Drama\"]','2020-04-20','6 min','https://m.media-amazon.com/images/M/MV5BMjUwNjg4NjUtODcwOS00NjZhLWIxNzgtYjg2YjYyN2VkY2IzXkEyXkFqcGdeQXVyNzg5MzIyOA@@._V1_SX300.jpg',1,'An aspiring writer befriends her boyfriend\'s sex doll and the two take on the 