ays away from the funerals,causing Leah to term him a coward. Nine months later Tom and Ethan appear in court but are cleared of causing death by dangerous driving though Tom\'s mother cannot forgive him and the others reject him. THough still on crutches it is Rachel who welcomes him back into the group as large numbers turn out to remember the deceased on the anniversary of the crash.'),(17,'Burning Crimes','[\"Nicolas Gob\", \" Salim Kechiouche\", \" Thomas Jouannet\"]','Christian Faure','Mikael Ollivier (novel), Franck Thilliez',6.4,'[\"Crime\", \" Drama\", \" Mystery\"]','2016-05-15','192 min','https://m.media-amazon.com/images/M/MV5BODYyZWQ0NmItYzkzYy00M2NmLWI1NzQtNTlkZjI5MmNiYTE2XkEyXkFqcGdeQXVyMzE2ODIxNA@@._V1_SX300.jpg',1,'The first big fire of the season ravages scrubland and forest. At the heart of the inferno, a burnt corpse is discovered in the smoking wreck of a 4X4. Others will follow, prompting brothers and rivals Guillaume and Damien, one a cop, the other a gendarme, to work together, whether they like it or not, to follow the trial of Tiffany, a renowned young photographer obsessed by fire. Or should they look into Târiq Amraoui, the Canadair pilot?'),(18,'Welcome Home','[\"Justin Alvis\", \" Mindy Miner\", \" Daniel B. Martin\"]','Justin Alvis, Bobby Chase','Justin Alvis, Bobby Chase, Daniel B. Martin, Amanda Stankavich',8.6,'[\"Comedy\", \" Family\"]','2015-08-08','25 min','https://m.media-amazon.com/images/M/MV5BMjNjNGY3MGItY2I1NC00MjE0LWJlZjMtMGJhZjE3MDY0NDE5XkEyXkFqcGdeQXVyMzgyODIzNjk@._V1_SX300.jpg',1,'When three thirty-somethings have no choice but to move back home with their parents, they realize a lot has changed since they\'ve been away.'),(19,'Contact','[\"Thomas Jouannet\", \" Alexis Loret\", \" Ingrid Donnadieu\"]','Frédéric Berthe','Hervé Korian',6.7,'[\"Action\", \" Crime\", \" Drama\"]','2015-12-17','48 min','https://m.media-amazon.com/images/M/MV5BYWMxOWVlOTctMmYyZS00MGEzLTk0YzQtMDc4OWNmMzk2MDM5XkEyXkFqcGdeQXVyMTg2MTEzMg@@._V1_SX3